The RTS logical track.
This class represents a single media (audio or video) in the RTS stream.
The RTS tracks are created automatically when the service notifies about the
sources becoming active, can be used to enable simple streaming scenarios:
enable projection of the audio and video coming from the same source with
lip-sync, with a single video renderer attached to the video track. When the
RTS source goes inactive, streaming for them is automatically disabled.
